quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  66,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  66,1,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum kyun uss cheez ko haraam karte ho jo Allah ne tumahray liye halal ki hai? ( kya is liye ke ) tum apni biwion ki khusi chahtay ho? Allah maaf karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  66,2,"Allah ne tum logon ke liye apni qasmon ki pabandi se niklny ka tareeqa muqarrar kar diya hai Allah tumhara Mooli hai, aur wohi Aleem o hakeem hai"
  66,3,"( aur yeh maamla bhi qabil tavajja hai ke ) NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ne aik baat apni aik biwi se raaz mein kahi thi phir jab uss biwi ne ( kisi aur par ) woh raaz zahir kar diya, aur Allah ne NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ko iss ( afshaye raaz ) ki ittila day di, to NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ne is par kisi hadd taq ( uss biwi ko ) khabardaar kya aur kisi hadd taq is se dar guzar kya phir jab NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ne ussay ( afshaye raaz ki ) yeh baat batayi to uss ne poocha aap ko iss ki kis ne khabar di? NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ne kaha,"" mujhe uss ne khabar di jo sab kuch jaanta hai aur khoob bakhabar hai """
  66,4,"agar tum dono Allah se tauba karti ho ( to yeh tumahray liye behtar hai ) kyunkay tumahray dil seedhi raah se hatt gay hain, aur agar nabi ke muqaabla mein tum ne baahum jatha bandi ki to jaan rakho ke Allah uss ka Mooli hai aur uss ke baad Jibreel aur tamam Saleh ahal imaan aur sab mulaika is ke saathi aur madadgaar hain"
  66,5,"baeed nahi ke agar NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam tum sab biwion ko Talaq daiday to Allah usay aisi biwiyan tumahray badlay mein ataa farma day jo tum se behtar hon, sachhi musalman, ba imaan, itaat guzaar, tauba guzaar, ibadat guzaar, aur roza daar, khuwa shohar deedaa hon ya bakrah"
  66,6,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, bachao apne aap ko aur apne ahal o Ayal ko uss aag se jis ka eendhan ensaan aur pathar hon ge jis par nihayat tund khoo aur sakht geer farishtay muqarrar hon ge jo kabhi Allah ke hukum ki nafarmani nahi karte aur jo hukum bhi inhen diya jata hai usay baja laatay hain"
  66,7,"( uss waqt kaha jaye ga ke ) ae kafroo, aaj m'azratay paish nah karo, tahein to waisa hi badla diya ja raha hai jaisay tum amal kar rahay thay"
  66,8,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, Allah se tauba karo, khalis tauba, baeed nahi ke Allah tumhari buraiyan tum se daur kar day aur tumhe aisijannaton mein daakhil farma day jin ke neechay nhrin beh rahi hon gi yeh woh din hoga jab Allah apne nabi ko aur unn logon jo is ke sath imaan laaye hain ruswa nah kere ga unn ka noor unn ke agay agay aur un ke dayen janib daud raha hoga aur woh keh rahay hon ge ke ae hamaray rab, hamara noor hamaray liye mukammal kar day aur hum se dar guzar farma, to har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
  66,9,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kufar aur munafiqeen se jehaad karo aur un ke sath sakhti se paish aao un ka thikana jahannum hai aur woh bohat bura thikana hai"
  66,10,"Allah kafiroon ke muamlay mein Nooh aur loot ki biwion ko bator misaal paish karta hai woh hamaray do Saleh bundon ki zojiat mein theen, magar unhon ne apne un shoharon se khayanat ki aur woh Allah ke muqaabla mein un ke kuch bhi nah kaam aa sakay dono se keh diya gaya ke jao aag mein jaane walon ke sath tum bhi chali jao"
  66,11,"aur ahal imaan ke maamla mein Allah firaon ki biwi ki misaal paish karta hai jabkay is ne dua ki"" ae mere rab, mere liye apne haan jannat mein aik ghar bana day aur mujhe firaon aur is ke amal se bacha le aur zalim qoum se mujh ko nijaat day """
  66,12,"aur Imran ki beti maryam ki misaal deta hai jis ne apni sharamgah ki hifazat ki thi, phir hum ne is ke andar apni taraf se rooh phoonk di, aur is ne apne rab ke arshadat aur is ki kitabon ki tasdeeq ki aur woh itaat guzaar logon mein se thi"
